  <acronym>Sanders IV</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Multicentre Clinical Trial Comparing Open Reduction Internal Fixation With Primary Subtalar Fusion in Patients With Severely Comminuted (Sanders IV), Displaced, Intra-articular Fractures of the Calcaneus</official_title>
